
> Gifting/Giving away items is not allowed
  unless the individual item value is not
  over &9$1 &fand the total given per day is 
  not over &9$100&f.

> You may not receive or purchase items
  from players that are breaking any of
  these posted rules.

> No selling items received from donations/kits
  but you can share them with your base mates.

> No selling items gained illegitimately.

> No selling items under the prices set by the
  market regulation document. You can find it
  by typing &6/market

> Trades must be between items of equal value.
  
> No selling of admin shop enchants.
  Vote chest enchants can be sold in original form 
  - not book form